::Fliq::

Breathing heavily, Fliq walks up to Iron Raptor, dropping Strafe in 
front of her. He transforms into robot mode.

"I recovered this bot from a wreckage up north," he says, gesturing 
toward the Decepticon, "What do you want to do with him?"
